text:
** Rewards Leaderboard Results ** 

* Top 10 has a bunch of usual suspects, but I hope that doesn't make us think less of their contributions to FC -- it's not on them that the algo put them there! 

* s/o @patriciaxlee.eth for a top 3, @marlo back in the top 10, & @priyanka  with back to back--her first 2! 

* @rocketman took his cobuild release to #12..congrats!; @derek  ($NATIVE guy) at #17, don't remember seeing him that high; & welcome @jennandtonic  at #21

* Meme-coveted #69 to /griv founder @igoryuzo.eth  after his first top 10 last week--which was better? ... not he narrowly edged out @jacy  (#68) who thinks #69 is the only spot that matters on the leaderboard!

* Keep an eye out for first-timers to celebrate with them üéà

show_title: Digital Pets and Irish Accents: GM Farcaster ep282
text:
What we're working on this week: 

1. Warplet improvements - price alerts for your favorite tokens, improving trending token filters.

2. New color scheme - giving the mobile app a little touch up. 

3. Tweaking the feed algo to recommend more interesting content. 

4. Lots of small improvements - fixed bugs with video, slow loading pages, miniapps etc. 

5. App-based storage - make it easy for apps to offer 'free' onboarding for Farcaster users.

text:
Sometimes I reflect on how lucky we all are to be debating frontier subjects like how creator coins accrue value or whether prediction markets reflect reality 

Most people are struggling these days (anecdotally) and the general economic climate is harsh. To feel secure and have bandwidth to work on this stuff is a gift

cast.text:
Are you buzzing about The @aptos Experience this October in Brooklyn? Us too.

Boys Club is an official media partner, and WE WANT YOU TO JOIN US ON THE GROUND!

We‚Äôre looking for a few community members to join our team there: capturing moments, sharing perspectives, or helping contribute to the best possible vibes. 

Whether your strengths are creative, operational, or just sheer enthusiasm, you are encouraged to apply.

Make your case at the link below by Sept 7th with a short note or video telling us what excites you most about The Aptos Experience and how you‚Äôd like to contribute.

Selected applicants will be chosen by Boys Club + Aptos Foundation on Sept 12 2025.

3 spots. Brooklyn, October 15-16. All expenses paid. Join us?
